{
  "page": "Great Bastards",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:452px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Great_Bastards_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/73/The_Great_Bastards_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/450px-The_Great_Bastards_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"251\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/73/The_Great_Bastards_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/675px-The_Great_Bastards_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/73/The_Great_Bastards_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/900px-The_Great_Bastards_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Great_Bastards_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Great Bastards by Jota Saraiva ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Great Bastards</b> was the nickname used to refer to the sons and daughters of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a> sired on <a href=\"/index.php/Nobility\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Nobility\">noblewomen</a>.\n</p><p>The Great Bastards were <a href=\"/index.php/Bastardy\" title=\"Bastardy\">legitimized</a> by Aegon while on his deathbed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Great_Bastards\">The Great Bastards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Great_Bastards&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Great Bastards\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon I Blackfyre\">Daemon Waters</a>, born to Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Daena_Targaryen\" title=\"Daena Targaryen\">Daena Targaryen</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_170_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">170&#160;AC</a>, later in life known as <i>Daemon I Blackfyre</i>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aegor_Rivers\" title=\"Aegor Rivers\">Aegor Rivers</a>, born to Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Barba_Bracken\" title=\"Barba Bracken\">Barba Bracken</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_172_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">172&#160;AC</a>, later in life known as <i>Bittersteel</i>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mya_Rivers\" title=\"Mya Rivers\">Mya Rivers</a>, born to Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Melissa_Blackwood\" title=\"Melissa Blackwood\">Melissa Blackwood</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_172_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">172&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_173_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">173&#160;AC</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gwenys_Rivers\" title=\"Gwenys Rivers\">Gwenys Rivers</a>, born to Lady Melissa Blackwood in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_173_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">173&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_174_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">174&#160;AC</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a>, born to Lady Melissa Blackwood in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_175_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">175&#160;AC</a>, later in life known as <i>Bloodraven</i>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shiera_Seastar\" title=\"Shiera Seastar\">Shiera</a>, born to Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Serenei_of_Lys\" title=\"Serenei of Lys\">Serenei of Lys</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_178_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">178</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184&#160;AC</a>, later in life known as <i>Shiera Seastar</i>.</li></ul>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Daena_Targaryen\" title=\"Daena Targaryen\">Daena<br />Targaryen</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:1em;heig